  "name": "South Wind's Scorch Song",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This <em>+1 striking flaming scimitar</em> is always warm to the touch, nearly unbearably so. Lines of crackling flame radiate from carnelians affixed to its curved and blackened blade, and its pommel ends in a brilliant tassel of phoenix feathers. While you have a status bonus to at least one of your Speeds, your Strikes with this scimitar that deal fire damage gain a +2 status bonus to their fire damage. The status bonus increases to +3 if the weapon has a greater striking rune and +4 for major striking.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.hy6LAC13QIJNDYXm]{Effect: South Wind's Scorch Song (Damage)}</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">f</span> command (evocation, fire, magical)</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your spell deals fire damage to a creature</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You gain a +10-foot status bonus to your Speed until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.eQqi3tWSHwV4SHqK]{Effect: South Wind's Scorch Song (Speed Boost)}</p>"
    },
